{"id":1493,"date":"2026-07-02T13:11:15","date_gmt":"2026-07-02T12:11:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/page_id=1493"},"modified":"2026-07-08T01:18:05","modified_gmt":"2026-07-08T00:18:05","slug":"industrial-cad-experience-bosch","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/industrial-cad-experience-bosch\/","title":{"rendered":"Industrial CAD Experience \u2013 Bosch"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1493\" class=\"elementor elementor-1493\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df956d4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"df956d4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-80d211e elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"80d211e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/cad_projects\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">\u2190 Back to 3D Printing Projects<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-efb2512 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"efb2512\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Industrial CAD Experience - Bosch<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b119fff e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b119fff\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3af25ae elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3af25ae\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>During my R&amp;D internship at Bosch, I designed and developed several custom mechanical components to support the development and testing of autonomous mobile robots. Working within a multidisciplinary engineering team, I contributed to projects involving robotic tooling, sensor integration, electronic packaging and charging infrastructure while considering manufacturability, assembly and system integration.<\/p><p>Due to the confidential nature of these projects, CAD models and photographs cannot be included.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-70a5394 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"70a5394\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dcfb62a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"dcfb62a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Project Information<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-293e979 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"293e979\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c9c669 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9c9c669\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Company<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Bosch<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Department<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Research &amp; Development<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Software<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Autodesk Inventor<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Project Type<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Industrial Robotics<\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5957935 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5957935\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-901df54 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"901df54\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Autonomous Robot Charging Station (Primary Project)<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a1a6b22 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a1a6b22\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4bad2ec elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4bad2ec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Over approximately two months, I contributed to the mechanical design and continuous development of a charging station for autonomous mobile robots. The project involved designing and refining components to ensure reliable mechanical alignment between the robot and the charging interface while supporting repeated docking during testing.<\/p><p>As the design evolved, I produced multiple CAD iterations, adapting components based on prototype evaluations and engineering discussions. This project gave me valuable experience working on a long-term industrial development project, where designs were continuously refined to improve functionality, manufacturability and integration with the overall robotic system.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e81549d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e81549d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Compliant Gripper Attachment<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb05fdc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eb05fdc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Designed a compliant mounting mechanism to connect a Schunk MPG-plus 25-IS gripper to an RSP STA20-4E tool changer. The mechanism incorporated precision guide rods and springs, allowing controlled movement along the Z-axis to absorb impacts while maintaining accurate positioning during manipulation.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f14d0f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f14d0f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Motor-Driven Nut Driver<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c83620 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5c83620\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Designed a custom attachment for a motorised assembly system to securely position and rotate nuts during an automated fastening process. The component ensured accurate alignment while providing a reliable connection to the motor shaft.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2ca25d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d2ca25d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">PCB Enclosure for Motor Electronics<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9522292 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9522292\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Designed a compact enclosure to house the motor&#8217;s printed circuit board within a constrained space. The enclosure incorporated cable routing channels, access openings for assembly and dedicated mounting features to securely retain the PCB.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d5049a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1d5049a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Reed Sensor Mount<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f949f7b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f949f7b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Designed a protective housing for a reed sensor used to detect the arrival of autonomous robots at an indexing station. The design included integrated cable routing, strain relief features and a mounting interface compatible with Bosch aluminium profiles, ensuring reliable installation in an industrial environment.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5957203 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5957203\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Engineering Skills Applied<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0ac634 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c0ac634\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li>Industrial mechanical design<\/li><li>Robotics integration<\/li><li>Mechanical assemblies<\/li><li>Sensor integration<\/li><li>Electronics packaging<\/li><li>Design for manufacturing (DfM)<\/li><li>Parametric CAD modelling in SolidWorks<\/li><li>Iterative product development<\/li><li>Collaboration within a multidisciplinary R&amp;D team<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rend